cilium-health completion 
 Generate the autocompletion script for the specified shell 
 Synopsis 
 Generate the autocompletion script for cilium-health for the specified shell.
See each sub-command's help for details on how to use the generated script. 
 Options 
   -h, --help   help for completion
 
 Options inherited from parent commands 
   -D, --debug         Enable debug messages
  -H, --host string   URI to cilium-health server API
 
 SEE ALSO 
 
 cilium-health 	 - Cilium Health Client 
 cilium-health completion bash 	 - Generate the autocompletion script for bash 
 cilium-health completion fish 	 - Generate the autocompletion script for fish 
 cilium-health completion powershell 	 - Generate the autocompletion script for powershell 
 cilium-health completion zsh 	 - Generate the autocompletion script for zsh
